{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.1", "text_original": "常棣之華，鄂不韡韡。凡今之人，莫如兄弟。", "text_normalized": "常棣之華，鄂不韡韡。凡今之人，莫如兄弟。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.2", "text_original": "死喪之威，兄弟孔懷。原隰裒矣，兄弟求矣。", "text_normalized": "死喪之威，兄弟孔懷。原隰裒矣，兄弟求矣。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.3", "text_original": "脊令在原，兄弟急難。每有良朋，況也永歎。", "text_normalized": "脊令在原，兄弟急難。每有良朋，況也永歎。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.4", "text_original": "兄弟鬩于牆，外禦其務。每有良朋，蒸也無戎。", "text_normalized": "兄弟鬩于牆，外禦其務。每有良朋，蒸也無戎。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.5", "text_original": "喪亂既平，既安且寧。雖有兄弟，不如友生。", "text_normalized": "喪亂既平，既安且寧。雖有兄弟，不如友生。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.6", "text_original": "儐爾籩豆，飲酒之飫。兄弟既具，和樂且孺。", "text_normalized": "儐爾籩豆，飲酒之飫。兄弟既具，和樂且孺。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.7", "text_original": "妻子好合，如鼓瑟琴。兄弟既翕，和樂且湛。", "text_normalized": "妻子好合，如鼓瑟琴。兄弟既翕，和樂且湛。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 7."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-luming-004__008__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-luming-004", "source_id": "xiaoya-luming-004__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·004.8", "text_original": "宜爾室家，樂爾妻孥。是究是圖，亶其然乎。", "text_normalized": "宜爾室家，樂爾妻孥。是究是圖，亶其然乎。", "notes": "常棣 Chinese stanza 8."}
